    75Ôćĺ
    76Ôćĺ  `Neverthrow` does not depend on any Node.js version-specific features, so it should work with any version of Node.js that supports ES6 and other runtimes like Browser, Deno, etc.
    77Ôćĺ
    78Ôćĺ  However, for the sake of maintaining a consistent development environment, we should declare the minimum supported version of Node.js in the `engines` field of the `package.json` file.
